    • Class mystars.entities.Lesson extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • day

          Day day
          The day of the week the lesson is conducted.

        • endPeriod

          int endPeriod
          Ending time for the lesson. See description for startPeriod. Must be larger than startPeriod

        • groupNo

          java.lang.String groupNo
          The group number assigned to the particular lesson (applicable for tutorials and labs).

        • index

          Index index
          The index that the lesson belongs to.

        • lessonType

          LessonType lessonType
          The type of lesson for this instance (i.e. lecture/tutorial/lab).

        • location

          java.lang.String location
          The location where the lesson is conducted.

        • startPeriod

          int startPeriod
          Starting time of the Lesson, from 0-31 where 0 represents 0800 and 31 represents 2330 respectively. Must be smaller than endPeriod (ie the lesson must start before it can end)

        • weeks

          boolean[] weeks
          Specific weeks the lesson will be conducted. boolean[13] representing whether the lesson is held in that particular week eg week[0] == false signifies that this lesson is not held in week 1
